SAPO-Broker version 0.01
========================

SAPO Broker perl client bindings.

See:
    http://softwarelivre.sapo.pt/broker
    http://softwarelivre.sapo.pt/projects/broker/wiki/Clients/Perl

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module depends on Thrift perl bindings.

You can get them at http://incubator.apache.org/thrift/download/

